.SH DESCRIPTION
.sp
\fI\%MPI_Comm_remote_size\fP determines the size of the remote group associated
with an intercommunicator.
.sp
The intercommunicator accessors (MPI_Comm_test_inter,
\fI\%MPI_Comm_remote_size\fP, MPI_Comm_remote_group) are all local operations.
